      "ja": "ここにずっと閉じ込められるの？",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic, do not panic.",
      "zh": "不要慌張，不要慌張。",
      "ja": "慌てるな、慌てるな。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are trained for professionals.",
      "zh": "我們是受過專業訓練的。",
      "ja": "私たちはプロとして訓練されている。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now stay calm, we are going around the leaf.",
      "zh": "現在保持冷靜，我們要繞過葉子。",
      "ja": "さあ落ち着いて、葉っぱの周りを回る。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Around the leaf?",
      "zh": "繞過葉子？",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周り？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think we can do that.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們做不到。",
      "ja": "それは無理だと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, nonsense.",
      "zh": "哦，胡說。",
      "ja": "そんな馬鹿な。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is nothing compared to the tweak of 93.",
      "zh": "這跟93年的小故障比起來算不了什麼。",
      "ja": "これは93年のトラブルに比べたら何でもない。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it, that's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣，就是這樣。",
      "ja": "そうだ、その調子。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good!",
      "zh": "好！",
      "ja": "いいぞ！",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're doing great!",
      "zh": "你做得很好！",
      "ja": "よくやってる！",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you go!",
      "zh": "就這樣！",
      "ja": "その調子！",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, you go!",
      "zh": "嘿，你去吧！",
      "ja": "さあ、行け！",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Watch my eyes, don't go away.",
      "zh": "看著我的眼睛，不要離開。",
      "ja": "私の目を見て、離れないで。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And here's the line again!",
      "zh": "線又來了！",
      "ja": "そしてまたラインだ！",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you!",
      "zh": "謝謝你！",
      "ja": "ありがとう！",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mr. Soil.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，土先生。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、土さん。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good job, everybody!",
      "zh": "大家做得好！",
      "ja": "みんな、よくやった！",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my, there's quite a gap, Mr. Soil.",
      "zh": "喔，土先生，這裡有很大的縫隙。",
      "ja": "おや、土さん、かなり隙間がある。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shouldn't we tell the queen?",
      "zh": "我們不應該告訴女王嗎？",
      "ja": "女王に知らせるべきじゃない？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think we need to involve the queen in this.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們不需要讓女王參與這件事。",
      "ja": "これに女王を巻き込む必要はないと思う。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's got enough on her plate already.",
      "zh": "她已經有很多事情要忙了。",
      "ja": "彼女はもう十分忙しい。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Trading her daughter.",
      "zh": "還要處理她的女兒。",
      "ja": "娘のことで手一杯だ。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yes, Princess Adam.",
      "zh": "哦，是的，亞當公主。",
